RESOLUTION

HPE has provided the following product updates to resolve the vulnerabilities
HPE Network Node Manager i (NNMi) Software:

 * Network Node Manager i 10.00:
 
  + Linux:
<https://softwaresupport.hpe.com/group/softwaresupport/search-result/-/facets
arch/document/LID/NNM1000L_00003>
  + Windows:
<https://softwaresupport.hpe.com/group/softwaresupport/search-result/-/facets
arch/document/LID/NNM1000W_00003>

* Network Node Manager i 10.10:
 
  + Linux:
<https://softwaresupport.hpe.com/group/softwaresupport/search-result/-/facets
arch/document/LID/NNM1010L_00025>
  + Windows:
<https://softwaresupport.hpe.com/group/softwaresupport/search-result/-/facets
arch/document/LID/NNM1010W_00025>

